title: Projects
description: Welcome to the projects section of Noodle Saddle

body.raw:
Projects section is built using ContentLayer and MDX.
### Go Lang web scrappers I started learning Go lang and as a first project I have built web scrappers. ### Chat Search project Utilizing the Open AI API, I have built a chat search project. ### Easy coding app for kids This is a personal project still working in progress. Please bear with me until I finish this project.
